    <keyword>Verify</keyword>
  </keywords>
  <body>
    <header>
      <para styleclass="Heading1">LFU Commands</para>
    </header>
    <para styleclass="Normal">At the <text styleclass="Code Example">UPD&gt;</text> prompt the utility presents a function menu. <text styleclass="Code Example">?</text> or <text styleclass="Code Example">Help</text> scrolls it:</para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"></para>
    <para styleclass="Code Example"> ***** Loadable Firmware Update Utility *****</para>
    <para styleclass="Code Example"> Function Description</para>
    <para styleclass="Code Example"> Display Displays the system&apos;s configuration table.</para>
    <para styleclass="Code Example"> Exit Done exit LFU (reset).</para>
    <para styleclass="Code Example"> List Lists the device, revision, firmware name, and update revision.</para>
    <para styleclass="Code Example"> Readme Lists important release information.</para>
    <para styleclass="Code Example"> Update Replaces current firmware with loadable data image.</para>
    <para styleclass="Code Example"> Verify Compares loadable and hardware images.</para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"></para>
    <para styleclass="Heading2">List</para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><text styleclass="Code Example">list</text> shows each device with its current revision, firmware filename, and the revision available to update to:</para>
    <para styleclass="Code Example">UPD&gt; list</para>
    <para styleclass="Code Example">Device Current Revision Filename Update Revision</para>
    <para styleclass="Code Example">nt Unknown nt_fw 5.71</para>
    <para styleclass="Code Example">srm 7.3-1 srm_fw 7.3-1</para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"></para>
    <para styleclass="Heading2">Display</para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><text styleclass="Code Example">display</text> prints the system configuration table (the same PCI / ISA inventory shown by <text styleclass="Code Example">show config</text> at the console). See show config and the Example - Performance transcript for the full layout.</para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"></para>
    <para styleclass="Heading2">Update</para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><text styleclass="Code Example">update &lt;device&gt;</text> replaces the named device&apos;s firmware in flash. Updating <text styleclass="Code Example">srm</text> refreshes the SRM console image; an unknown device name is rejected (&quot;not supported under LFU&quot;).</para>
    <para styleclass="Code Example">UPD&gt; update srm</para>
    <para styleclass="Code Example">Confirm update on:</para>
    <para styleclass="Code Example">srm [Y/(N)]y</para>
    <para styleclass="Code Example">WARNING: updates may take several minutes to complete for each device.</para>
    <para styleclass="Code Example"> DO NOT ABORT!</para>
    <para styleclass="Code Example">srm Updating to 7.3-1... Verifying 7.3-1... PASSED.</para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal">When done, <text styleclass="Code Example">exit</text> leaves LFU (a reset) and the firmware continues to the <text styleclass="Code Example">&gt;&gt;&gt;</text> prompt.</para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><text styleclass="SeeAlso">See Also.</text></para>
